\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(There might be a battle. Let's change clothes to
prepare for battle...)

What the hell, it's like an empty shell as if they
were never really here.

I can feel warmth on the bed, and there's a scent
too. There's no doubt that someone was here until
recently.

So, did they know we were coming and run away? How
did they...?

Who knows. But, she's a 'witch', right? Maybe
there are various magical techniques like that.

Besides, it's possible that today was just a
coincidence. Anyway, let's go already.

Ugh, I thought since she dressed so provocatively,
I might as well have a quick fuck while I'm at it.

\n<Thief A>Who the hell are you!! What are you doing here
without permission!

\n<Thief A>What the hell is this slut!? Does she want to be
fucked?!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>That outfit, 'Dark Owl'...! \.Is this also a
scheme by the demons!?

\n<Thief B>Tch, causing a commotion. Fine, I'll take care of
you!
\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I'll listen to your story slowly inside the cell!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>It was really helpful that the guard came close
by! It would be tough to carry that thief all the
way to town.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Thank you so much for helping me this much. I
wonder how I can repay you...
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Ehehe, it's fine! Please don't worry about it!

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>And besides, I also obtained some fragments. If we
investigate these, we might be able to find the
location of another device!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>Is it really okay? We're really grateful for your
help, but...

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Yes! It's a great opportunity for me to
investigate such an interesting magic power! We
both have something good to gain from this!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I see... Thank you very much. \. I will pay the
reward all at once.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>By the way, Rain-san, is your body okay? You
received 'Nightmare Heaven' again, right?

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────...\....\ ....\.I'm fine now. I took a little
rest, so...

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>This magic is probably the type that slowly erodes
even if it's defended with magic power. If it were
to directly hit, the burden on the body would be
quite significant.

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I will investigate the new fragments, so please
rest properly. It will take some time, at least
until tomorrow!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I'm sorry for causing you worry. Meryl-san, please
don't push yourself too hard.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Yes! Then please come again \C[17] starting from
tomorrow \C[0]!

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[83]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(─────As Meryl-san said, the burden on my
body is intense... \. It was definitely not good
to directly receive 'Nightmare Heaven' again...)

\CE[78]\CE[79]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(I can feel my desires... swelling... My body and
mind quickly become filled with lewd
sensations...)

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[83]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Calm down... Take a deep breath... ───── As
\. said, for now, let's rest our body...)

Thank you very much for playing up to this point.
The main story that can be progressed in the trial
version will end here.

You can continue to enjoy the trial version by
exploring the town and returning to the dungeon
afterwards.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Um, I heard there was a 'witch' here, so I came to
visit... Is it you?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Witch's Daughter>Yes! I'm still inexperienced, but I've been
allowed to be a witch!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>I am Rain, a holy knight of the royal capital. I
have something to discuss...
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Witch's Daughter>H-Holy knight!? A-Are you here to capture me...!?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Witch's Daughter>I-I haven't done anything wrong!! It's true that
there may be witches like that, but the research
I'm doing isn't harmful, and even receiving
magical power is done properly───

\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Please calm down, I didn't come here to capture
you. Rather, I came to make a request.

\OC[25]\N<Witch's Daughter>Is that true? My master taught me that holy
knights despise witches...

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>It's true, I won't capture you without reason.
While there may be religions that do so, the Holy
Magic Church we belong to doesn't engage in such
things.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Witch's Daughter>I-I see. I'm sorry, I recently left my master's
side, so I don't know much about the world...
\CE[78]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Don't worry. I swear to the Holy Magic God.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Witch's Daughter>In that case, that's great! Ah, my name is Meryl!
I stopped by this town during my training journey!
Nice to meet you!

\CE[79]\CE[84]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(This is quite unexpected... I always thought
witches had a gloomier image, but I guess it
varies from person to person.)
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>So, you have a favor to ask me, right?

\OC[31]\N<Rain>I would like to ask for your help in investigating
this fragment...

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>────There's quite a creepy magical power lingering
here. What is this?

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I thought there was hardly any magical power left,
but do you see it?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Of course, I can see! From my perspective,
there's still plenty of it lingering.

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I may not be as skilled as my master, but I'm
quite good at capturing residual magical power!

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>That's reassuring. What I want to know is about
that magical power and the magic that was
generated from the fragment...
Rain explained the circumstances to Meryl.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I see... There are even bad people involved! To
think they would involve the entire town!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Understood! It seems like it will be a good
training opportunity, so I'll take on this
investigation! I'll borrow this fragment for a
while!
\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Thank you very much. How much will the reward be?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Reward? I don't need that kind of thing~. I'm
still inexperienced, after all!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>I can't do that. This is a request as a holy
knight, in other words, a request from the
country. Doing it without compensation would
affect the trust of the country.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>But, I see... This is a job after all... \.─\.
Hmm, actually, this is my first time working as a
witch.......... I wonder how much should I charge
for it.
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I've got it! I just came up with a great idea!

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>While I was passing through this town, I was
thinking of collecting research materials in the
surrounding forest.

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>However, one of the materials I want is a bit
troublesome to obtain. How about this as a reward
instead? You help me gather it for me!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I see. Understood, that's fine. I'm actually good
at physical work, so it works out.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Yay! Thank you so much! Well then, please take
care of it!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I'll summarize the details in a memo! While you go
and gather it, I'll continue with the
investigation!
\OC[31]\N<Rain>Nice to meet you. Well then, I'll be going too.

Now you can go to the Hakusei Forest from the
world map.

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Meryl-san, sorry to keep you waiting. I've brought
the pufferfish eggs.
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Thank you very much! I appreciate it!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Here it is! The testicles of an Energetic Monkey!
\. It can be used as medicine and has strong
effects as an aphrodisiac!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Ah, but I'm sorry... the investigation of the
fragments isn't finished yet... \. It's quite
difficult to extract them...

\CE[83]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>It's okay. I didn't expect the investigation to be
finished so easily.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>It's taking longer than I thought, but it looks
like it will be finished by tonight. So, \C[17]
can you come back again \C[0] tomorrow or later?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I understand. But please don't push yourself too
hard.

\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Well, since I have time until tomorrow, should I
go around \C[17] town or take a rest at the
dormitory...
'Explore the town or take a rest at the inn'

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I'm not the most physically capable, so I
appreciate it! I'll continue with the
investigation of the fragments!

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I will finish it by tonight, so \C[17]please come
again \C[0]tomorrow or later!
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Ah, Rain-san! Hello! I've been waiting for you!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Hello. You seem to be in a good mood, is something
going on?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>It's not like something happened, but I've been
having fun investigating the magical power trapped
in that fragment! I've made so many interesting
discoveries, and my magical research is
progressing really well!

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>You've brought something so interesting, I want to
thank you so much for it!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Hmm, I'm not really well- versed in magic, so I
can't fully understand. But if you're happy about
it, then that's great.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I've become able to analyze and detect the magical
power trapped in this fragment. For now, what I've
found is that the same magical power can be sensed
from three other locations.

\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Three locations...! So, that means there are at
least three more 'Nightmare Heaven' generators...

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Since I detected a fairly strong magical power,
the possibility seems high.

\OC[31]\N<Rain>─────Do you know where you were able to detect
that magical power?

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Since I was only able to analyze a small amount of
magical power, I can't say for certain, but I can
sense one in the northwestern direction from here.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I'm sorry, but I think if I had more magical power
samples, I would be able to clarify things
further. But for now, this is the limit...

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>No, just knowing that there is a possibility of
other devices is already a significant gain. In
fact, it's impressive that you were able to
investigate with just these fragments.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I'll investigate if there are any suspicious
places in the northwestern direction on my end!
Thank you very much!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>The magic embedded in this fragment... It's called
'Nightmare Heaven'. It seems to be a pretty
powerful spell... Rain, are you okay...?

\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(If it's about the Hakudeti area, Kardo might
know. Let's go to the guard station and ask.)
'Lets ask about the northwest at the guard station'
\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Please be careful and come back safely.

\N<Meryl>Please make sure to rest well and come back
\C[17]tomorrow or later\C[0], okay!

\N<Meryl>Please make sure to rest well and come back
\C[17]tomorrow or later\C[0], okay!

\CE[79]\CE[78]\N<Meryl>Ah~ So that's how it's structured. How
interesting...

\CE[79]\CE[78]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Seems like she's completely absorbed in her
research. I should leave her alone.)

\CE[79]\CE[78]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Meryl-san, you seem really sleepy... Are you
perhaps not getting enough sleep?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Ahaha, when I find something interesting, I forget
to sleep. But it was worth it, because I roughly
figured out the location of another device!
\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Amazing! As expected of you.\. So, where is it──?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>It's in the southeast, I think it's probably
\C[17]Tachimate Beach\C[0].

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>There's an old dungeon that was sealed there a
long time ago, so I think that's probably it.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Since it's quite a famous place, I went there out
of curiosity before coming here. But now it has
become like a tourist spot and I couldn't get in.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>A tourist spot... I see. It could be the perfect
place to hide the device, couldn't it?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Ah, but it's not confirmed! I'm sorry if I'm
wrong...

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>No, not at all. Just knowing that it's located in
the southeast is already a great achievement.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>However, we need to enter and confirm that old
dungeon, so let's go there right away.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I understand... Ah... I'm sorry, I'm already at my
limit with sleepiness...

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Please rest well. Thank you for investigating
until you became sleep deprived.

We can now go to Tachimate Beach from the castle
gate.
'Investigate the dungeon located at Tachimate Beach'
